# BLoC Pattern

## BLoC vs Cubit

- **BLoC**: complex flows (auth, sockets, multi-step forms, paginated lists)
- **Cubit**: simple UI state (toggles, tab index, form visibility)

## File Structure

```
presentation/blocs/{feature}/
├── {feature}_bloc.dart
├── {feature}_event.dart
└── {feature}_state.dart
```

## Rules

- States and events are immutable — use Equatable
- No business logic in widgets — only in BLoC/Cubit/UseCase
- Side effects (navigation, snackbars): `BlocListener`
- UI rebuilds: `BlocBuilder` or `BlocSelector`
- Register BLoCs in `presentation/di/presentation_layer_injection.dart`
- App-level BLoCs via `MultiBlocProvider` in `main.dart`
- Feature BLoCs via `BlocProvider` at route/screen level when needed
